s-and-Rivers-03.jpg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Roads-and-Rivers-03.jpg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Roads-and-Rivers-03.jpg 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/Roads-and-Rivers-03.jpg 2400w\"></figure><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Rivers go with the flow... where we surrender and become part of our environment.\"</blockquote><p>Collection size: 30 artworks (25 stills, 5 motion)<br />Eth: 0.25 ea</p><p><a href=\"https://foundation.app/collection/roadsandrivers\">View Roads and Rivers on Foundation</a> </p><p><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/roads-and-rivers\">View Roads and Rivers on OpenSea</a></p><hr />"}